      <p>SmartyPants Men's Complete dominates this list because no other men's gummy multivitamin delivers this many clinically relevant nutrients in a single product. The formula combines omega-3 DHA and EPA (288mg from sustainably sourced fish oil for cardiovascular and cognitive health), CoQ10 (for mitochondrial energy production that declines with age), lycopene (the carotenoid shown to support prostate health in multiple epidemiological studies), zinc (11mg for testosterone production and immune function), vitamin D3, a complete B-complex, and vitamin K2.</p>

